{"lemma":"دَرَجَة","slug":"دَرَجَة","root":"د.ر.ج","root_slug":"د-ر-ج","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ر-ج","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"دَرَجَة","root":"درج","pos":"N","occurrence_count":18},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12387","n12388","n12389","n12390","n12393"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stair, step"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stairway, staircase"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"degree","tags":["general"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"degree, rank, order, dignity, condition, station"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mark, grade (at school)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stage upwards (to Paradise, etc.)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/da.ra.d͡ʒa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12387","headword_ar":"دُرْجَةٌ","root":"drj","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing which is rolled up, and inserted into a she-camel's vulva, and then"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taken forth, whereupon"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she smells it, and, thinking it to be her young one, inclines to it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and yields her milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) or, accord. to Aboo-Ziyád El-Kilá- bee, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of rags,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of tow and rags"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and other things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is rolled up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and stuffed into a she-camel's vulva,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and into her tuel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and bound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when they desire her to incline to the young one of another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having first bound her nose and her eyes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) they leave her thus, (S, K,) with her eyes and nose bound, (K,) for some days, (S,) and she in consequence suffers distress like that occasioned by labour: then they loose the bandage [of her vulva] from her, and this thing comes forth from her, (S, K,) and she thinks it to be a young one; and when she has dropped it, they unbind her eyes, having prepared for her a young camel, which they bring near to her, and she thinks it to be her own young one, and inclines to it: (S:) or with the thing that comes forth from her they besmear the young one of another she-camel, and she thinks it to be her own young one, and inclines to it: (K:) the thing thus rolled up is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durojapN","text_ar":"دُرْجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jazomN","text_ar":"جَزْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waviyqapN","text_ar":"وَثِيقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T;) and the thing with which her eyes are bound,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gimaAmapN","text_ar":"غِمَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and that with which her nose is bound,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiqaAEN","text_ar":"صِقَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) the pl. [of mult.] is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durajN","text_ar":"دُرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) and [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoraAjN","text_ar":"اَدْرَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or it signifies [or signifies also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a piece of rag containing medicine, which is put into a she-camel's vulva when she has a complaint thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durajN","text_ar":"دُرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L, K.) ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of rag stuffed with cotton, which a woman in the time of the menses puts into her vulva,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to see if there be any remains of the blood:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MF:) likened to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drjp","text_ar":"درجة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a she-camel. (K.) It is said in a trad. of 'Áïsheh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kun~a yaboEavona biAAld~arajapi fiyhaA Alkurosufu","text_ar":"كُنَّ يَبْعَثْنَ بِاالدَّرَجَةِ فِيهَا الكُرْسُفُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They"},{"kind":"text","text":"(women)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used to send the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drjp","text_ar":"درجة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with cotton therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (IAth, K, * TA:) but accord. to one reading it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dirajap","text_ar":"دِرَجَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAth, K,) pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durojN","text_ar":"دُرْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[explained above], meaning “ a thing like a small"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safaT","text_ar":"سَفَط"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which a woman puts her light articles and her perfumes: ” (IAth:) El-Bájee read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajap","text_ar":"دَرَجَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", which seems to be a mistake. (K.) ―         -b3-  See also 4, last sentence.       -A2-  And see what here next follows."}],"source_refs":["S","T","K","M","TA","MF","IAth"]},{"entry_id":"n12388","headword_ar":"دَرَجَةٌ","root":"drj","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A single stair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"step, of a series of stairs"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a ladder; one of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraj","text_ar":"دَرَج"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sul~am","text_ar":"سُلَّم"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) and hence, by a synecdoche, (Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a series of stairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a ladder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Mgh, Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"constructed of wood or of clay"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against a wall or the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by which one ascends to the roof of a house;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durajapN","text_ar":"دُرَجَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durojapN","text_ar":"دُرْجَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duraj~apN","text_ar":"دُرَجَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoruj~apN","text_ar":"اَدْرُجَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the pl. of the first is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajN","text_ar":"دَرَجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or [rather]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajapN","text_ar":"دَرَجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[has for its proper pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَجَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and] is n. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajN","text_ar":"دَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabapN","text_ar":"قَصَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabN","text_ar":"قَصَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajN","text_ar":"دَرَجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَجَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stages upwards:"},{"kind":"text","text":"opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakN","text_ar":"دَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَكَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَجَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used in relation to Paradise; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَكَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in relation to Hell. (B voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darakN","text_ar":"دَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A degree"},{"kind":"text","text":"in progress and the like: you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajapF darajapF","text_ar":"دَرَجَةً دَرَجَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"By degrees; gradually."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A degree, grade,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"order, of rank"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dignity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K: *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"degree, grade, rank, condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"station:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exalted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"high, grade"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَجَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K, TA.) ―         -b4-  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A degree of a circle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thirtieth part of a sign of the Zodiac:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَجَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b5-  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A degree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"four minutes, of time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajaAtN","text_ar":"دَرَجَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","S","A","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n12389","headword_ar":"دُرَجَةٌ","root":"drj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph.       -A2-  Also, (ISk, S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dur~ajapN","text_ar":"دُرَّجَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain bird,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which the inside of the wings is black, and the outside thereof dustcoloured; in form like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaTaA","text_ar":"قَطَا"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but smaller,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"more slender:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S:) thought by IDrd to be the same as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dur~aAj","text_ar":"دُرَّاج"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dar~aAjapN","text_ar":"دَرَّاجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence.]"}],"source_refs":["ISk","S","K","Sb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n12390","headword_ar":"دُرَجَّةٌ","root":"drj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajapN","text_ar":"دَرَجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n12393","headword_ar":"دُرَّجَةٌ","root":"drj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durajapN","text_ar":"دُرَجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}